## 7. Data Flow Summary

```
Transcript Data (JSON)

quantizeTranscript()  align to frame boundaries

loadWords()  extract words array

loadTranscript()  render timestamps + transcript text

User selects text in UI

addHighlightStrip()  create highlight with word_indices

onZoomsChangeCallback('add')  JSX execution

addZoomAtTimeAndCenterAsymmetric() in Premiere

zoomClipsChangeListener()  polls for changes

getZoomClipsAccordingToSequence()  compare state

Update local zooms array
```

